name: PHOTO - HENOWEEN 3 "LOST FAMILY"
description:
[zoom in to the bottom right...]

This is a photo of a lost family.
They are searching for a landmarks
but nothing leads them home.
The child cries, the mother holds
the water jug -- nearly empty.

They are lost in the centuries.
Can you guide them?
Can you help them find their home?
HAPPY #HENOWEEN
